#: ../../../firmware-guide/acpi/video_extension.rst:7
msgid ""
"This driver implement the ACPI Extensions For Display Adapters for "
"integrated graphics devices on motherboard, as specified in ACPI 2.0 "
"Specification, Appendix B, allowing to perform some basic control like "
"defining the video POST device, retrieving EDID information or to setup a "
"video output, etc.  Note that this is an ref. implementation only.  It may "
"or may not work for your integrated video device."
